==Etymology==
From Latin ''[[decimalis]]'', from ''[[decem]]'', '''ten''' + adjective suffix ''[[-alis]]''

==English==
===Adjective===
'''decimal'''

#(''mathematics, computing'') Concerning mathematical calculations performed using [[base]] 10.

====Translations====
* Dutch: [[decimaal]]
* [[Esperanto]]: [[dekuma sistemo]]
*{{msg:fi}} : [[desimaali-]], [[desimaalinen]]
* French: [[nombre décimal]]
* German: [[dezimalsystem]] oder [[zehnersystem]]
* Japanese: [[10進数]]
